  "description": "A wide-angle view presents a cityscape silhouetted against a warm, golden sunrise or sunset. The skyline is dominated by modern skyscrapers, with a prominent, pointed structure being the tallest. In the foreground, a rugged, rocky terrain is covered in golden, dry grasses and weeds. Scattered debris and construction materials are visible, suggesting a transitional or industrial area. A chain-link fence partially obscures the view, adding a sense of distance and separation. The overall atmosphere is hazy and ethereal, with the light creating a soft, glowing effect on the buildings and vegetation.",
